          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill requires the Department of the Treasury to define the dollar in terms of a fixed weight of gold, based on that day's closing market price of gold. The Federal Reserve Banks shall&nbsp;make Federal Reserve notes exchangeable with gold at the statutory gold definition of the dollar.</p>]]></text>
